text: Shinnosuke Oka (born 31 October 2003) is a Japanese artistic gymnast. In 2019, he won two gold medals, one silver medal and one bronze medal at the 2019 Junior World Artistic Gymnastics Championships held in Győr, Hungary. He won the gold medal both in the team event and in the men's all-around event.
